<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema513_08_su_0007_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema513_08_0007.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema513_08.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema513_08_su_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 3">
          <span class="blue line" lang="y">내 힘으로 풀어요</span>
          <span lang="y">공부한 내용을 확인해요</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="title type3 jgjd_3_sub_title">
        <h2 lang="y"><span>[5~7]</span>예준이가 육각형과 삼각형을 이용하여 규칙적인 배열을 만들고 있습니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="title type2 jgjd_3_sub_title">
        <h2 data-head="6_pink" lang="y">서로 대응하는 두 양을 각각 기호로 나타내고, 두 양 사이의 대응 관계를 기호를 사용하여 식으로 나타내어 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="img_box">
          <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA513_08_SU/0006_content.png" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="question_box multiple_answers">
          <div class="line line1">
            <span lang="y">육각형의 수를</span>
            <div class="input_wrap answer1">
              <math-field data-answer-single="□"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span lang="y">, 삼각형의 수를</span>
            <div class="input_wrap answer2">
              <math-field data-answer-single="△"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span lang="y">(이)라고 할 때, 두 양 사이의</span>
          </div>

          <div class="line line2">
            <span lang="y">대응 관계를 식으로 나타내면</span>
            <div class="input_wrap answer3">
              <math-field class="multiple_input1" data-answer-single=""></math-field>
            </div>
            <span lang="y">=</span>
            <div class="input_wrap answer4">
              <math-field class="multiple_input2" data-answer-single=""></math-field>
            </div>
            <span lang="y">입니다.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="multiple_map" hidden>
            <div data-multiple="1" data-input1="△" data-input2="□+1"></div>
            <!-- △=□+1 -->
            <div data-multiple="2" data-input1="□" data-input2="△-1"></div>
            <!-- □=△-1 -->
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
